        "timestamp": "2021-10-15 18:04:06.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6: Code-Review-1\n\n(2 comments)\n\nI reviewed DCAEGEN2-2819 (and it's parent task DCAEGEN2-2906). Neither of those really say what is being added for each feature. For example, what is expected to be in the JSON file and what do the different fields mean?\n\nThey essentially just say \"add these features\", but there're no pointers to a description of what changes are required to support those features.\n\nWhere is there such a description? Is there a wiki page that can be pointed to in the JIRA tickets? Or some other review? There's an mp4 file pointed at in the comments of DCAEGEN2-2819, but it is inaccessible.\n\nHow can I tell whether the proper stuff is being implemented without this information?",
